Package main.java.vlashchevskyi.exam.request

Contains classes that represent booking requests, provide treats to read, create, compare and group booking requests.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BookingRequest
    BookingRequest is interface represents wrapped booking request.
    Splitter
    Splitter is interface contains the method to split unsorted booking requests dependent on their date.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseBookingRequest
    BaseBookingRequest class implements methods to wrap, compare booking requests.
    BookingTimeComparator
    BookingTimeComparator class is comparator compares booking requests by booking time.
    RequestComparator
    RequestComparator is abstract class to compare booking requests.
    RequestFactory
    RequestFactory is factory to create requests by condition.
    RowBookingReader
    RowBookingReader class reads booking requests as sequence of String and build row booking requests.
    RowBookingRequest
    RowBookingRequest class represents original row booking requests.
    SortedSplitter
    SortedSplitter class implements the method to sort and split booking requests.
    SubmissionTimeComparator
    SubmissionTimeComparator class is comparator compares booking requests by submission time.
    UnsortedSplitter
    UnsortedSplitter class implements the method to split unsorted booking requests.

Package main.java.vlashchevskyi.exam.request Description

Contains classes that represent booking requests, provide treats to read, create, compare and group booking requests.
